creator: EasyApp Developer
descriptionHtml:
ABOUT US:
IIT Ashram began its journey in the year 2004. Started as an institution preparing students to compete in IIT JEE (Indian Institute of Technology Joint Entrance Examination). IIT Ashram now has widened its horizon. Now it offers courses for JEE Main(AIEEE), JEE Advanced(IIT-JEE), NEET(AIPMT), AIIMS, GUJCET and Foundation courses for the students of Secondary School.

The primary objective of the institute is to build a strong knowledge base in Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics and Biology among students to enable them to face the competitive world.

The strength and success of the institute lies in its highly qualified, dedicated and experienced teaching staff who have been handpicked from premier institution in the country.


MISSION
To prepare outstanding professionals in the field of engineering and medicine who would be nationally competitive and internationally acclaimed.

VISION
To serve as a valuable resource for society; focus on excellence in education; address the needs of the present and the challenges of the future and remain a source of pride for society.

OUR VALUE
Honesty, Integrity, Humanity, Loyalty, Devotion and Compassion are some values that run in the Ashram stream.
descriptionShort: Best Institute for IIT/JEE preparation in Vadodara, Gujarat. Since 2004
